Package: LDRegularization
Type: Package
Title: Regularization of Linkage Disequilibrium Matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yihe Yang
Maintainer: Yihe Yang <yxy1234@case.edu>
Description: This package provides methods for regularizing large-scale 
    linkage disequilibrium (LD) matrix. It implements a variety of 
    regularization techniques, including shrinkage, nonlinear shrinkage,
    banding, tapering, thresholding, standard POET extensions, and
    cluster-wise POET for LD matrices. The package enables efficient
    computation for high-dimensional LD matrix estimation via
    CppMatrix-backed matrix operations where possible.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    CppMatrix
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
